# Per-user trust profile storage directory
# Each user gets a subdirectory with their UUID containing:
# - trust_profile.json (psychological trust model)
# - attachment_state.json (attachment stage history)
# - interaction_history.json (key moments, trust events)
# - emotional_memory.json (user-specific emotional tags)
#
# Example structure:
# psychology/users/
#   rodrigo_specter/
#     trust_profile.json
#     attachment_state.json
#     interaction_history.json
#   user_abc123/
#     trust_profile.json
#     attachment_state.json
#     interaction_history.json
#
# This directory is auto-populated by TrustProfileManager class
